人話睇成報係戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果cc台班糞青有能力搞武裝革命搞港獨,我又唔會笑9佢地<br />\n依家又唔係叫佢地班垃圾求雜種<br />\n只係中立分析下件事都講到求緊人咁"},{"pid":"8a3d5d3c4b417f3a8b731ffb43db973fd14f5f97","tid":136163,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報警有用咩？</blockquote><br />\n奴位充係對頭派既馬,都知重案唔會做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92ae83d79eae24c631d648f85c74de42acdbbdb","tid":136163,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:27:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁樣做野姐係話比人聽係真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擺到明兩派人鬥緊，係唔知點解仲有人唔相信，好似中共建國幾十年無試過內鬥咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCC台班垃圾中央又唔讀<br />\n仲以為共產黨係好撚團結<br />\n<br />\n遠d既有 林彪 劉少奇 彭德懷<br />\n近d有趙紫陽,胡耀邦<br />\n再近d有薄熙來,周永康"},{"pid":"4acde305b82470e0961d9fa2c1439558654edf31","tid":136163,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T07:51:46.000Z","msg":"幾時斬人同連人帶車燒?"},{"pid":"03014b4a0888050d8a3870043b09309a78ffa6fa","tid":136163,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T08:02:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁樣做野姐係話比人聽係真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擺到明兩派人鬥緊，係唔知點解仲有人唔相信，好似中共建國幾十年無試過內鬥咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nCC台班垃圾中央又唔讀<br />\n仲以為共產黨係好撚團結<br />\n<br />\n遠d既有 林彪 劉少奇 彭德懷<br />\n近d有趙紫陽,胡耀邦<br />\n再近d有薄熙來,周永康</blockquote><br />\n中共由建黨開始就已經一直無停過內鬥啦，唔係點會俾毛澤東條仆街上到位"},{"pid":"4295edc34c43